  "time_ut": 1657307535,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0b92\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0ba4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Conspiracy by spies to turn protest into violence",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "We will extend our full support to the struggle in Khalimugathil. We will continue this struggle and oust the government. The government plans to turn the peaceful protest into violence and crack down. People's Liberation Front General Secretary Rilvin Silva said that conspiracies could be carried out to provoke violence by deploying government spies in the middle of the protest.",
        "He said this at a press conference organized by National People's Power in Colombo yesterday (8).",
        "The government has failed to solve the country's problems, government services have collapsed, medical infrastructure has collapsed, education has stalled, people have come to the streets, and the queues are increasing day by day. This increases deaths. Therefore, a situation has developed in which the people of the country cannot survive. Insensitive rulers have ruined the country.",
        "The whole country should unite and fight continuously till we oust this government. The only solution is to expel them. We will extend full support to the protest tomorrow (today). We will continue this struggle and oust the government.",
        "There are suspicions that there is a plan to create violence between the protests. Government agents may attend meetings and create confusion. So we request people not to resort to violence under any circumstances. We inform the government that the whole country is fighting against one team and this cannot be stopped through manoeuvres.",
        "He said that if there is any violence in any place, the government should take the overall responsibility."
      ],
